OL,3,CBroadcaster John Stapleton announces
OL,4,CParkinson's disease diagnosis
OL,6,FBroadcaster John Stapleton has
OL,7,Frevealed he has Parkinson's disease.
OL,9,FThe 78-year-old, who has presented on
OL,10,Fprogrammes including Newsnight,
OL,11,FPanorama and GMTV's News Hour, said
OL,12,Fthe disease can be "very frustrating"
OL,13,Fon BBC One's Morning Live.
OL,15,F"Speaking is how I've earned my living
OL,16,Ffor the best part of 50 years," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
