OL,3,CBroadcaster John Stapleton announces
OL,4,CParkinson's disease diagnosis
OL,6,FSpeaking about his mother, Stapleton
OL,7,Fsaid: "I witnessed my mother's decline
OL,8,Ffrom this lively, ebullient, outgoing
OL,9,Flady to a lady who is fairly fragile.
OL,11,F"One of the practical problems she
OL,12,Ffaced initially was her inability to
OL,13,Fdo things like open a can of beans or
OL,14,Fpeel a potato.
OL,16,F"Believe it or not, I'm having the
OL,17,Fsame problem, to some extent, myself
OL,18,Fright now."
