OL,3,CBroadcaster John Stapleton announces
OL,4,CParkinson's disease diagnosis
OL,6,FSpeaking to his son, Stapleton said
OL,7,Fthat he wishes to remain "independent"
OL,8,Ffor as long as possible and he would
OL,9,Fbe "reluctant" to leave his house.
OL,11,FIn a post to X, charity Parkinson's UK
OL,12,Fsaid: "A huge thank you to
OL,13,F@JohnStapletonTV for his announcement
OL,14,Fon @BBCMorningLive following his
OL,15,FParkinson's diagnosis.
OL,17,F"We want to offer our support to John
OL,18,Fand his son, @staplenick, as they
OL,19,Fstart John's unique journey with the
OL,20,Fcondition."
